levelRequirements.name: Power User
levelRequirements.privilege: uploaded at least 5 torrents,can access notifications and collage subscriptions, create new collages, get a personal collage, access to the Power User & Invites forums, can create forum polls, use the artist and personal Collector features, can access profile page stat graphs, and immunity from inactivity disabling.

levelRequirements.name: Elite
levelRequirements.privilege: uploaded at least 50 torrents, Access to the Elite forum, Top 10 filters, a second personal collage, profile album, and torrent editing privileges.

levelRequirements.name: Torrent Master
levelRequirements.privilege: uploaded at least 500 torrents, Access to the Torrent Master forum, earns custom title, a third personal collage, the ability to omit their username from personal collage names, and unlimited invites.

levelRequirements.name: Power TM
levelRequirements.privilege: uploaded at least 500 torrents,Everything Torrent Master gets plus a fourth personal collage.

levelRequirements.name: Elite TM
levelRequirements.privilege: uploaded at least 500 torrents,Everything Power TM gets plus a fifth personal collage.
